; error.moof — Result-based error handling
;
; no try/catch. errors are values: { Err message: "..." }
; use Result (Ok/Err) for operations that can fail.
; use recover: on Results and Acts for error handling.
;
; (err "message") creates an Err value.
; [result ok?] checks if it succeeded.
; [result recover: |e| fallback] handles errors.

(defn err (msg) { Err message: msg })
